						<summary>

						<p>Slab in the well near the mosque in the <hi rend="italic">bazār.</hi></p>						

						<p>Circa 14th century.</p>						

						<p>The record states that the well as also the Mayilārdēva-<hi rend="italic">chatra</hi> were constructed by Ayipadēva-ayya.</p>						

						<p>It is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="italic">Āṅgira, Mārggaśira,</hi> other details not being given.</p>						

